  Version bump.

  30 Mar 2013; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org> libsecret-0.14.ebuild:
  Policy fixups, switch to python-any-r1.

  05 Mar 2013; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org> -libsecret-0.11.ebuild:
  Clean up old revision.

